
Ranger Help for: improvise
==========================

SYNTAX:      improvise
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   12
BASE SP:     110 sp
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
With this skill, a Ranger has an advantage over his or her opponent.
He or she may improvise an attack by noting his or her surrounding
terrain and use it to their advantage. The Ranger must already be
attacking in order to improvise. 

